Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
nielson.c195projectmkn.Models.Appointment
public class Appointment extends Object
Author:
mckaykn The appointment class represents customers appointments made, using ID, title, descriptions, location, type, start time, end time, create date, who the appointment was created by, when it was last updated, who was it last updated by, customer, user, and contact
